snippet.title: Alien Armageddon 2.0 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Official trailer for version 2.0 of the Alien Armageddon TC for Duke Nukem 3D. Release date is February 16th, 2019 and it will be available for download at Mod DB: www.moddb.com/mods/duke-nukem-alien-armageddon

This is a huge update that includes our remaster of Duke it Out in DC, and much more new content.
The rendition of the Star Spangled Banner used in this video is by Iced Earth.
